5A202CB1.Line1.6DE47: Lorath and Donan have gone to Caldeum. The Knights march on the city. They felt it best to follow.

608DBF14.Line11.BAE4: I try. Yet my best isn’t enough. Not for Yorin, nor your mother.

7337041C.Line19.BAE4: It can, with a good ally.

8F55D8A7.Line25.6DE47: We should go. I’ll find the others in Caldeum.

A31403C6.Line15.6DE47: Can I ask you something? Something personal.

C1F212B9.Line9.6DE47: Do you ever feel like nothing you do matters?

DD9C3BA7.Line5.BAE4: More than I’d like to admit. They call me hero. But underneath, I’m still the same person I always was. Powerful, sure. But flawed, too.

F414A633.Line3.6DE47: But I wanted to wait for you.

F5615F25.Line23.6DE47: (exhale) Thank you. For being honest. It helps...knowing I’m not alone.
